 *
 * @return `NOTMUCH_STATUS_OUT_OF_MEMORY: Out of memory.`
 *
 * @return `NOTMUCH_STATUS_FILE_ERROR: An error occurred trying to open the
 *	database or config file (such as permission denied, or file not found,
 *	etc.)`
 *
 * @return `NOTMUCH_STATUS_XAPIAN_EXCEPTION: A Xapian exception occurred.`
 *
